//
//	ARGUMENTS:
//	_this:				OBJECT	- vehicle for which the ammo is counted
//
//	RETURNS:
//	_this:				SCALAR	- number between 0 and 1 corresponding to the relative ammo count
//
//	Example:
//	_vehicle call Achilles_fnc_getVehicleAmmoDef;
